            }
          ],
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "When one of the Guests dies, its body collapses into a tangle of meat, gristle, fur, bone, and gore. Creatures within a 10-foot emanation (other than other Guests) must make a DC 22 Will save to avoid becoming sickened 2 (sickened 4 on a critical failure) at the sight and smell.",
